---
import karen from "../assets/Karen.jpg";
---

<section id="about" class="bg-[color:var(--bg)]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10 sm:py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] md:items-stretch">
      <!-- Texto -->
      <div
        class="rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--border)] bg-[color:var(--panel)] p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8 flex flex-col"
      >
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[color:var(--text)] sm:text-3xl">
          Karen Barragán
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--muted)] text-justify">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing, elit fermentum
          sodales purus ultrices a, eu vitae vulputate quam netus. Velit aliquet
          consequat magna facilisi pellentesque facilisis cras, torquent vitae
          leo proin eu ultricies vivamus ad, habitant arcu urna tellus malesuada
          mus. Ultricies laoreet nec habitasse facilisis proin facilisi risus
          diam aenean, ut ligula turpis primis orci magnis per duis, nibh
          penatibus class pulvinar ornare purus eu consequat.
          
          Montes aliquam
          turpis ligula commodo hendrerit senectus facilisis venenatis dictumst,
          cum est facilisi erat etiam tempor augue mauris aptent, donec dui at
          lacinia mi quisque interdum sodales. Nam donec fames ridiculus
          condimentum neque risus ac ligula tempus suscipit conubia ad nostra
          tellus justo, integer id sociosqu per habitasse mollis pulvinar eu
          rhoncus himenaeos torquent tempor etiam ut. Malesuada proin diam
          dignissim ultrices per odio sed, luctus senectus hendrerit porttitor
          ante fames imperdiet tellus, mollis placerat egestas facilisis
          accumsan feugiat.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a class="k-btn-brand hover:brightness-110" href="#contacto"
            >Agendar cita</a
          >
          <a class="k-btn-surface hover:opacity-90" href="#servicios"
            >Ver servicios</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Imagen -->
      <div
        class="rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--border)] bg-[color:var(--panel)] p-3 shadow-sm sm:p-4 flex items-center justify-center"
      >
        <div
          class="w-full max-w-sm overflow-hidden rounded-xl aspect-[4/5] sm:aspect-[3/4] md:aspect-[4/5]"
        >
          <img
            src={karen.src}
            alt="Karen Barragán - Karitiana"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
